data.description: Welcome to the charm of urban living with this 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home located at 2382 Ridgecrest Ln in East Point. Spanning 1068 sq ft, this property offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle in a vibrant neighborhood.    Inside, you'll find a welcoming layout with three cozy bedrooms, each providing a private and peaceful space for relaxation. The bathroom is efficiently designed for daily convenience. The heart of the home is the living area, which is both warm and inviting, perfect for family time or entertaining guests.    The kitchen is a standout feature, offering functionality and a seamless flow into the main living spaces. It's an ideal setup for those who love to cook and dine in a comfortable setting.    At the rear of the property, there's a modest yet charming yard, providing a quaint outdoor space for relaxation or activities. This area adds a pleasant touch to the home, enhancing its appeal.    One of the unique aspects of this property is the additional space in the unfinished basement. This area presents a fantastic opportunity for customization, whether you envision a home office, a workout room, or extra storage space. The possibilities are endless, allowing you to tailor this extra space to your personal needs and style.    Located in a lively East Point neighborhood, this home is part of a community known for its spirited and friendly atmosphere. The area has a close-knit feel, offering a blend of city excitement and community warmth.    2382 Ridgecrest Ln is more than just a house, it's a home with and charm, situated in a neighborhood full of life and energy. It's the perfect choice for anyone looking to embrace the dynamic spirit of Atlanta while having a space to enjoy.
